      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To instruct the United States Governor of, and the United States Executive Director at, the International Monetary Fund to use the voice and vote of the United States to advocate that the Fund not recognize the government of the Islamic Republic of Afghanistan under Taliban control, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
